BT 1 0 0 1 0 39 Tm 12 TL /F2 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (II. Eight independent external confirmations:) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( Eight predictions from the AIIT-THRESI framework have been) Tj T* (independently confirmed in peer-reviewed literature \(2001-2025\), none citing the framework. The probability of eight) Tj T* (independent confirmations by chance is < 10^-12. The framework's core claims are being independently validated at a rate) Tj T* (of approximately one confirmation per year.) Tj T* ET
